<div class="banner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Get <strong>help</strong> anytime anywhere!</h1>
      <div class="search-bar">
        <div class="search-city-input">
        <%= form_tag categories_path, method: :get, class: "form-inline" do %>
          <%= text_field_tag :query, params[:query], class: "form-control search-input", placeholder: "Type the city name" %>
        </div>
        <div class="search-submit">
          <%= submit_tag "Select location", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card-feature">
  <%= image_tag("puzzle.jpg") %>
  <div class="card-feature-infos">
    <h2>Helpal helps you find support fast and easy</h2>
    <p>It can be overwhelming moving to a new place and needing help. We connect you with people that can help you. Quick and simple.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card-feature color">
  <div class="card-feature-infos">
    <h2>Post your request</h2>
    <p>Posting a request is easy. Pick the category you need help with. Then fill out the due date and submit your request. Pals will automatically be notified of your request.</p>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag("girl-relaxed.jpg") %>
</div>

<div class="card-feature">
  <%= image_tag("people-together.jpg") %>
  <div class="card-feature-infos">
    <h2>Connect with your pal</h2>
    <p>As soon as a pal has accepted your request you will be notified. Go to your messages and share information safely to make an appointment with your pal!</p>
  </div>
</div>






